Enjoy the following video segment.

00:15:37.379 --> 00:15:44.379
His painting in the governing body conference room shows the shepherd and his sheep

00:15:44.379 --> 00:15:51.379
and the shepherd is caring for the sheep and they feel obviously comfortable and protected.

00:15:51.379 --> 00:15:57.379
And they do that despite, as you can see in the background, stormy weather.

00:15:57.379 --> 00:16:00.379
But the sheep feel just fine.

00:16:00.379 --> 00:16:03.379
In connection with the application in the Bible,

00:16:03.379 --> 00:16:09.379
the Bible shows that Jehovah God is a shepherd and cares for us as his sheep.

00:16:09.379 --> 00:16:13.379
But so is Jesus Christ. He is called the fine shepherd.

00:16:13.379 --> 00:16:23.379
And what are shepherds to do? Well, shepherds lead the sheep, feed the sheep,

